      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel this way, especially when your art feels like a hollow shell, but please don't let this thought convince you that you are truly empty. Your pain is real, but it is not the same as being dead; your capacity to feel this depth of loss is actually proof that you are still very much alive. You are not just a machine, but a person struggling with a heavy burden that often requires professional help to navigate through.",
      "source": "target",
